 @koen1232  are you like not even watching the footage look at the STRAIGHT WHITE DOTTED LINES they indicate a lane for road cars to drive in you can see perez go from the middle of the painted line to slightly more left of the painted line meanwhile you can see carlos who wasn’t on the white line move closer to the white line meaning perez moves away from carlos and carlos moves towards perez

btw the racing line for that turn is to hug the wall to get a better exit through turn 3 not drift into the middle of the track 

